name beamertheme-geode
category Package
revision 79040
shortdesc A colourful modernised style package for beamer documents
longdesc This style package aims to provide a new, modernised style to
longdesc beamer class documents, loosely inspired by minerals, and
longdesc features multiple colour palettes as well as the ability to
longdesc create new ones.
